snippet.title: Yaoling: Mythical Journey | Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Formerly known as Home of the Yokai, Yaoling: Mythical Journey is a creature collecting Eastern fantasy RPG featuring an expansive world filled with rich stories, interesting characters, and over nearly 300 unique Yaolings. On your journey across the Land to become a Yaoling Keeper you will traverse through uncharted lands, encounter many never-before seen Yaolings, and form new friendships. Yet, a looming evil is spreading, and many Yaolings are succumbing to its corruption. The peaceful lives of the Yaolings are in jeopardy, are you ready for what is to come?
_______________________________________________________________

Follow us for updates!
